name: Kasumi - DOA6 - Character LORA
description:
Trained on NAI with 80 pictures (mostly 3d fanart). Versatile lora (anime, semi-realistic, 3D, realistic)
Best result with weight between : 0.8-1.

Prompt activator : kasumi \(doa\)
Other prompt : brown hair, long hair, ponytail, bare shoulders, arm guards, pelvic curtain

Torn clothes prompt : torn clothes, dirty, ripped clothes

For full body pictures, sometimes you will need to inpaint the face because it can be distorted.

Commissioned by ocelot1300 on fiverr

Reviews are really appreciated, i love to see the community use my work, that's why I share it.
If you like my work, you can tip me here.

Got a specific request ? I'm open for commission on my fiverr gig *! If you provide enough data, OCs are accepted

*Any paid request will not be presented on this page, unless you give me permission to.
